==English==
===Noun===
'''socket'''

# An opening into which a [[plug]] or other connecting part is designed to fit (e.g. ''a [[lightbulb]] socket'').
# In [[anatomy]]:
#* The part of a [[joint]] that recieves a [[bone]].
#* A [[hollow]] into which a part (e.g. [[eye]]) fits.

